Mr. Clerk, please call the roll.

3
00:00:13,244 --> 00:00:13,865
Councilor Collins.

4
00:00:14,785 --> 00:00:15,106
Present.

5
00:00:15,286 --> 00:00:15,926
Councilor Seng.

6
00:00:15,966 --> 00:00:16,347
Present.

7
